{"tid":1710964,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"香港同志遊行仍等待警方發出「不反對通知書」","createTime":"2019-11-12T09:23:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-14T05:53:12.000Z","uid":240362,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"ffecd5f9bb7e2fbab70ad7af31fe1943edbcac84","tid":1710964,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T09:23:46.000Z","msg":"Hong Kong Pride Parade 香港同志遊行<br />\n1 小時 &middot;<br />\n<br />\n【#hkp2019】2019年11月12日 大會通告<br />\n<br />\n香港同志遊行2019仍等待警方發出「不反對通知書」，按法定情況，最遲有可能會於14號下午才收到。<br />\n<br />\n本籌委會相信，市民應享有和平表達訴求的權利，我們亦十分珍視同志爭取平權的發聲權利。故此，本籌委會仍繼續爭取在11月16日舉辦公眾活動，同時也繼續做好所有事前的準備工作。我們收到最新情況後，將第一時間對外發放。<br />\n<br />\n各位希望參與11月16日香港同志遊行的朋友們，請留意本籌委會公佈的消息。"},{"pid":"606e49c932bdb06f932cb1c3340085ccb34ffad0","tid":1710964,"uid":312125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T09:25:19.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">［文宣入！］返工搭鐵受襲、催淚彈影響健康、女學生返學俾狗捉，<strong>請文宣製圖向怕死嘅打工仔、家長、學生宣傳三罷</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n林鄭連續兩日叫大家唔好罷工罷課，證明罷工罷課係佢春袋，然而差佬不斷製造罷工罷課條件，文宣請行動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n請文宣組以<span style=\"color: red;\">今日黑警突襲旺角站無差別襲擊勤力返工人士</span>、<span style=\"color: gold;\">尋日中午中環射催淚彈</span>、<span style=\"color: red;\">今日警察街上捉返學嘅女學生</span>、<span style=\"color: gold;\">以及警察話上堂等於非法集結</span>，做罷工罷課文宣圖<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">警告堅持要返工返學嘅人，即將面對惡犬強姦殺人滅口嘅危險，在網上廣傳！</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/nbQFJcX\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/nbQFJcX</a><br />\n#131 回覆"},{"pid":"00866ba86b003a0b3b96d6611637de8c0a066c1d","tid":1710964,"uid":330472,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T09:28:54.000Z","msg":"香港人報仇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n要攬炒，出去燒藍店<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n自然唔搞中大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c56284b4db28244973e201d9d4634c893fa39a8","tid":1710964,"uid":127858,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T05:37:56.000Z","msg":"反極權 撐同志<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06339152e8ab3312044046cc137eb75aede5f3dc","tid":1710964,"uid":65253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T05:52:08.000Z","msg":"撐自己人"},{"pid":"5c9525c1f3d7f172065850bda44270e45bf91bc1","tid":1710964,"uid":147047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T05:53:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}